The paper discusses the challenges of integrating interactive proof features into an automatic program verifier, specifically in the context of the SPARK environment for critical software development. This involves extending the Why3 verification toolchain with interactive proof features and a generic client-server infrastructure for integration with external graphical user interfaces. The paper touches on topics related to software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), logic (cs.LO), embedded systems (cs.ET), and formal methods (cs.FL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.SE, followed by cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.ET, and cs.FL.
